thread.title: FOREX-Dollar rises on Atlanta Fed chief's rate view
thread.title_full: FOREX-Dollar rises on Atlanta Fed chief's rate view | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: FOREX-Dollar rises on Atlanta Fed chief's rate view
text:
NEW YORK Aug 4 The dollar climbed to session highs against the yen and euro on Tuesday after the Wall Street Journal published online an interview with Atlanta Federal Reserve President Dennis Lockhart who said the Fed is "close" to being ready to hike rates.
The greenback was last up 0.1 percent at 124.13 yen, while the euro hit a session low against the dollar at $1.0922 .
(Reporting by Richard Leong )
